--- title: "Demographics (patient information)" execute: freeze: auto --- The cleaning script used here is at: [GitHub: mover, 01_patient_information.R](https://github.com/SurgicalInformatics/mover/blob/main/01_patient_information.R) ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} library(tidyverse) library(finalfit) source("functions.R") theme_set(theme_bw()) demographics = read_csv("/home/common/mover_data/surginf_cleaned/patient_information_cleaned.csv") demographics_orig = read_csv(paste0(Sys.getenv("epic_emr"), "patient_information.csv"), col_select = c("MRN", "LOG_ID")) ``` ::: The patient information dataset includes 39,685 patients who had 64,354 surgeries. The original file has 65,728 rows, removing duplicate patient ID (`mrn`) and procedure ID (`log_id`) rows, leaves us with 64,354 patient-procedure observations. Variable list: [MOVER: Patient Info Table](https://mover.ics.uci.edu/patient-info-table.html) Automatically generated data dictionary, including interactions and missingness: [pointblank::scan_data(demographics)](https://argoshare.is.ed.ac.uk/mover_pointblank/) ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} demographics %>% mutate(across(all_of(c("sex", "primary_anes_type_nm", "patient_class_group")), fct_infreq)) %>% summary_factorlist(explanatory = c("age", "sex", "los", "primary_anes_type_nm", "asa_rating", "patient_class_group")) %>% kable() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} |label |levels |all | |:--------------------|:------------------------------------------------|:------------| |age |Mean (SD) |55.2 (17.5) | |sex |Male |34214 (53.2) | | |Female |30139 (46.8) | | |Unknown |1 (0.0) | |los |Mean (SD) |7.4 (14.3) | |primary_anes_type_nm |General |51748 (80.5) | | |Monitored Anesthesia Care (MAC) |5112 (7.9) | | |Moderate Sedation - by non-anesthesia staff only |3630 (5.6) | | |Regional |2518 (3.9) | | |None |510 (0.8) | | |Local |363 (0.6) | | |Epidural |284 (0.4) | | |Spinal |113 (0.2) | | |Choice Per Patient on Day of Surgery |38 (0.1) | | |Topical |2 (0.0) | |asa_rating |Brain Dead |41 (0.1) | | |Healthy |2960 (5.1) | | |Incapacitating Disease |6370 (11.1) | | |Mild Systemic Disease |18068 (31.4) | | |Moribund |657 (1.1) | | |Severe Systemic Disease |29449 (51.2) | |patient_class_group |Inpatient |41070 (63.8) | | |Outpatient |23284 (36.2) | ::: ::: # Length of stay ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} demographics %>% summary_factorlist("los", "patient_class_group", cont = "median") %>% kable() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} |label |levels |unit |value | |:-------------------|:----------|:------------|:-----------------| |patient_class_group |Inpatient |Median (IQR) |6.0 (2.0 to 13.0) | | |Outpatient |Median (IQR) |0.0 (0.0 to 1.0) | ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} demographics %>% drop_na(los) %>% ggplot(aes(los, fill = patient_class_group)) + geom_histogram(binwidth = 1) + facet_wrap(if_else(los>50, "LOS > 50 days", "LOS < 50 days")~patient_class_group, scales = "free", ncol = 1) + scale_x_continuous() + scale_fill_viridis_d() + theme(legend.position = c(0.9, 0.95)) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](demographics_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=960} ::: ::: # Procedures ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} demographics %>% count(primary_procedure_nm, sort = TRUE) %>% # Changing from ALL CAPS to lowercase mutate(primary_procedure_nm = str_to_sentence(primary_procedure_nm)) %>% mydt(pagelength = 50) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: :::
